title: Patrick Mahomes, Cowboys-Eagles, Tom Brady, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Patrick Mahomes, Cowboys-Eagles, Tom Brady, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin gives his reasons why he feels the Chiefs should worry about being to reliant on Patrick Mahomes, why the loser of the Cowboys-Eagles game might be fine, why Tom Brady will win the AFC again, and his new Blazing 5 picks. Guests include Rashad Jennings, Eric Dickerson, Urban Meyer, T. J. Houshmandzadeh, and Jason McIntyre.
